


Create Host:

Single Host:
	a. Storage Tab --------> Host section -------> Click + symbol ----------> Create Host
	Enter Hostname and click create
	
Multiple-Hosts:
	a. Storage Tab --------> Host section -------> Click + symbol ----------> Create Host ------> Select multiple hosts
	
	Enter Hostname (ESX#), Start number, Count, and Number of digits, and click create
	
	
	
	
	
	
	ADD Host ports to Host:
	
	Open Created Host --------> Go with Host port tab --------> + Symbol ----------> If discovered below select otherwise add WWNs or iSCSI
	
	Ex: Configure WWNs, IQNs, NQNs
	
	
	Create Host Group:
	
	i. Storage Tab --------> Host section -------> Click + symbol ----------> Create Host Group
	Enter the Host group name and click create
	
	Open Host Group -------> Add hosts to host group 
	
	
	
	
	
	
